output_summary.title: Laptop Warranty Certificate
claimable_items: Motherboard, RAM Modules, CPU (Processor), Solid-State Drives (SSDs) / Hard Drives (HDDs), Internal Cooling Fans, Display Panel (non-accidental damage), Keyboard and Trackpad, Wireless Network Card
non_claimable_items: Battery (limited warranty to 12 months from purchase date), External Adapters and Charging Cables, Cosmetic Damage (scratches, dents, paint wear), Accidental Damage (liquid spills, drops, burns), Unauthorized Hardware Upgrades or Modifications, Pre-installed or Third-Party Software Issues
